# sin BD en Streamlit Cloud. Ver docs/desarrollo/16_DEPLOY_STREAMLIT_CLOUD.md.
# Excluimos solo staging y backups dentro de processed/.
data/processed/_backup_scope_*/
data/processed/_staging/
data/*.json
data/mongo_local/
backups/

